{"tid":2167562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"別再，像極了偷情 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-08-21T07:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T07:53:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55284769f8b0a5e359bc78eec05b469f9ebce08a","tid":2167562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/AZ4HBTXXXVG55G2IERG6FDEOBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FAZ4HBTXXXVG55G2IERG6FDEOBM%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=0f069b0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FAZ4HBTXXXVG55G2IERG6FDEOBM%2F&h=f4f837eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/AZ4HBTXXXVG55G2IERG6FDEOBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n別再，像極了偷情 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sFic0EOsw74I6ZmbsVm8yzm2hgs=/3623x2321/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SED3QVRP5JEYVE5QRBFOIDEY4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsFic0EOsw74I6ZmbsVm8yzm2hgs%3D%2F3623x2321%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSED3QVRP5JEYVE5QRBFOIDEY4M.jpg&h=ca1f6f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我冇立場嘅，延任一年，誓要去，抑或留，極多聲音分析留的壞處，但走頭之後，可以點呢？聲音即刻玩抖音，甩鍋說：到時見招拆招啫。噢，公定字，都你贏。<br />\n<br />\n咁啦，講吓去留肝膽乜乜乜，好冇？<br />\n<br />\n留，議員被神秘車隊啄住，蓄意辣㷫你。走人，跟蹤的「傳媒」唔單止被差佬放生，還會撩你打交，拍晒獨家。柒周後，上門拉人告你煽動恐嚇兼污衊国安。<br />\n<br />\n留，差佬與立法會保安聯手，用招呼鄺俊宇的膝跪頸秘技，關愛泛民議員。走人，便衣差佬大隻過你柒倍，無喇喇告你打爆咗佢塊臉的痱滋。<br />\n<br />\n留，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n留，見外國使節是日常。走人，冇議員身份就係勾結外國勢力。（除非個外國勢力是平壤政府）<br />\n<br />\n留，。。。。。。。。走人，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n留，唔係WFH，名正言順出糧。走人，斷糧意料中事，唔係689，預咗冇五千萬分手費，絕對唔會將立法會當做康橋咁再別。別再，像極了偷情。"},{"pid":"6cf5211903ae0ee16725e30f25dec1025d274317","tid":2167562,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T07:53:15.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<br />\n<br />\n已經唔能夠用文章 / 只能用詩詞 去盲撐泛民議員延任臨立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}